author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
We're back with The Indie Hour Episode Thirty-Two! This series focuses on games you may have never even heard of and gives us an inside look at the wider world of independantly published Tabletop Wargames of all genres.

Love GOD OF WAR? Big fan of JASON AND THE ARGONAUTS? Just can't get enough of XENA or JOXOR THE MIGHTY? Chris Bahnweg has the game for you in DEMIGOD, where you take the role of a Greater Hero of myth and fight the legends of ancient times. Let's dive in! 

Check out the rulebook in digital  HERE: https://no-name-games.com/demigod/
title: The GMG Indie Hour Ep 032 - DEMIGOD by Chris Bahnweg
